{"tid":2250661,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"如何令狗狗安享晚年","createTime":"2020-10-20T09:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T03:39:21.000Z","uid":71166,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"37e290fc9fb3691dc6fe6c80e5a935b39096992c","tid":2250661,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:03:40.000Z","msg":"我狗。唐種 10歲 女<br />\n性格溫純乖巧<br />\n不幸有乳線瘤<br />\n醫生指已到後期 狗狗年紀大了<br />\n手術要十萬及成功只得4成機會<br />\n因此未能做手術<br />\n昨日在診所狗狗亦很友善活潑<br />\n亦有不斷親吻護士和走時歡送我家人的朋友<br />\n接回家後她顯現不開心<br />\n因為她以後要帶上頭套和扎肚<br />\n暫時狗狗肺很健康 但淋巴有陰影不知是什麼<br />\n要每日服藥和扎肚"},{"pid":"79bae1e6b1a95a660f8e53c3fcbc784d3d7f6c70","tid":2250661,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔想講<br />\n但係盡量減低佢嘅痛楚係最好嘅決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a8e0984b50b38c0f02988f846951b630f90307","tid":2250661,"uid":71166,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:05:54.000Z","msg":"請問有沒有補健藥和中醫療程介紹<br />\n希望可舒緩她的不適<br />\n狗狗胃口很好 近數年已換了鮮食<br />\n但醫生希望她吃乾糧較好<br />\n請問有介紹嗎"},{"pid":"fcd9067200c83b8361e498a97d6361c173430154","tid":2250661,"uid":212460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:06:07.000Z","msg":"狗狗加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef352a4abb80f1a45fbb8675da277df446524ce7","tid":2250661,"uid":38543,"like":1,"dislike":40,"score":-39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:06:25.000Z","msg":"養左咁耐  食左佢"},{"pid":"a620782adb8b229cb8521775caf5cdb2ab384de6","tid":2250661,"uid":364798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\